  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Semantic grouping:</strong> Helps assistive technologies identify summary rows</li>
      <li><strong>Navigation:</strong> Screen reader users can jump directly to the table footer</li>
      <li><strong>Implicit role:</strong> tfoot has an implicit ARIA role of <code>rowgroup</code></li>
      <li><strong>Clear labels:</strong> Use descriptive text like "Total" or "Average" in the first cell</li>
    </ul>
